{"tid":1650384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵所有線路正常輕鐵部分路線改道","createTime":"2019-10-13T02:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T02:43:12.000Z","uid":333676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbeb5122cb3b297e0c149e20422c4890c6b7c1a","tid":1650384,"uid":333676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:38:50.000Z","msg":"港鐵今早晨所有鐵路線服務正常, 列車服務提早於今晚十時結束。在九龍塘站, 昨日被投擲汽油彈的出入口繼續封閉。 列車服務維持正常, 港鐵指, 個別車站仍有不少設施有待修復。除機場快線外, 各線列車服務提早於今晚十時結束。 輕鐵所有線路恢復行駛, 部分路線改道, 車輛唔會行經友愛﹑天榮、銀座﹑天湖﹑天慈及天水圍站。 機場快綫下午三时起只來往機場及香港站。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oTb5mU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oTb5mU.png&h=a3836bbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a04580191b42f075925616af8c97bf93ade790ae","tid":1650384,"uid":297334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnfFehm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnfFehm.png&h=1d978c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEzyzhm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEzyzhm.png&h=9f7f7645&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SqRkXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SqRkXn.png&h=23325b93&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}